net.grinder.statistics
Class TestStatisticsMap

java.lang.Object
  net.grinder.statistics.TestStatisticsMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
Externalizable, Serializable
public final class TestStatisticsMap
extends Object
implements Externalizable

A map of test numbers to StatisticsSets.

Test statistics synchronisation occurs at the granularity of the contained StatisticsSet instances. The map is synchronised on the TestStatisticsMap itself.

Author:
Philip Aston
